comment_data.body: @stevemessick : thoughts on this?  Should we even install into Webstorm?
WebStorm is not supported. Not sure why it allowed the plugin to be installed, but this combo won't work.
Thanks for the report @bigidea-kz.  Unfortunately, we do not currently support WebStorm.  How did you install the plugin?

Hello
https://plugins.jetbrains.com/plugin/9212-flutter
I downloaded from this link and placed in the plugins folder
